---

---

<section class="bg-gray-50 py-16 lg:py-24" aria-labelledby="neden-biz-baslik">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2
                id="neden-biz-baslik"
                class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 inline-block relative pb-3"
            >
                Neden Biz?
                <span
                    class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-20 h-1 bg-primary rounded-full"
                ></span>
            </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Item 1 -->
            <div
                class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group text-center flex flex-col items-center"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-50 text-primary flex items-center justify-center rounded-3xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 shadow-sm group-hover:shadow-md"
                >
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass text-3xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                    İhtiyaç Analizi
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    İşletmenizin veya mekanınızın tente veya branda
                    ihtiyaçlarını doğru bir şekilde analiz ederek, size en uygun
                    çözümleri sunmak için buradayız.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 2 -->
            <div
                class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group text-center flex flex-col items-center"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-50 text-primary flex items-center justify-center rounded-3xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 shadow-sm group-hover:shadow-md"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        height="40"
                        viewBox="0 96 960 960"
                        fill="currentColor"
                        width="40"
                    >
                        <path
                            d="M166 936v-94h127L187 480q-32-15-50-40.5T119 372q0-47 34.5-81.5T235 256q44 0 73 23.5t39 62.5h146v-59q0-12 9-21t21-9q11 0 18.5 8.5T549 281l75-72q8-8 20.5-10.5T670 202l158 76q9 5 12.5 14t-1.5 19q-5 10-14.5 12t-18.5-3l-155-75-98 99v52l98 103 155-76q10-5 19-2.5t14 12.5q5 10 1.5 20T827 468l-153 72q-14 7-27 6.5T624 536l-75-72q0 14-7.5 21t-18.5 7q-12 0-21-9t-9-21v-60H345q0 12-6.5 24.5T323 447l205 395h158v94H166Zm69-508q24 0 40-16t16-40q0-24-16-40t-40-16q-24 0-40 16t-16 40q0 24 16 40t40 16Zm124 414h102L272 475q-3 2-10 4t-11 3l108 360Zm102 0Z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Üretim</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    İhtiyacınıza göre uygun ve kaliteli malzemeler kullanarak
                    üretim sürecini hızlı bir şekilde gerçekleştiriyoruz.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 3 -->
            <div
                class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group text-center flex flex-col items-center md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 md:w-1/2 lg:w-full md:mx-auto"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-50 text-primary flex items-center justify-center rounded-3xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 shadow-sm group-hover:shadow-md"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        height="40"
                        viewBox="0 96 960 960"
                        fill="currentColor"
                        width="40"
                    >
                        <path
                            d="M764 976q-6 0-11-2t-10-7L501 725q-5-5-7-10t-2-11q0-6 2-11t7-10l85-85q5-5 10-7t11-2q6 0 11 2t10 7l242 242q5 5 7 10t2 11q0 6-2 11t-7 10l-85 85q-5 5-10 7t-11 2Zm0-72 43-43-200-200-43 43 200 200Zm-569 72q-6 0-11.5-2t-10.5-7l-84-84q-5-5-7-10.5T80 861q0-6 2-11t7-10l225-225h85l38-38-175-175h-57L80 277l99-99 125 125v57l175 175 130-130-67-67 56-56H485l-18-18 128-128 18 18v113l56-56 169 169q15 15 23.5 34.5T870 456q0 20-6.5 38.5T845 528l-85-85-56 56-52-52-211 211v84L216 967q-5 5-10 7t-11 2Zm0-72 200-200v-43h-43L152 861l43 43Zm0 0-43-43 22 21 21 22Zm569 0 43-43-43 43Z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Montaj</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    İhtiyaçlarınızın montajını hızlı ve kaliteli bir şekilde
                    gerçekleştiriyoruz. Tecrübeli ve uzman ekibimiz sayesinde,
                    ihtiyaçlarınızı en iyi şekilde karşılayacak çözümler
                    sunuyoruz.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
